title: Cisco Devices: Temperature Sensors {CISCO-ENTITY-SENSOR-MIB}
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/cisco
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors all temperature sensors for Cisco devices
 that support CISCO-ENTITY-SENSOR-MIB.
 It uses a combination of data from the standardized
 sensors MIB and vendor specific information.

 Upper warning and critical levels are retrieved from the device
 via SNMP or can be set in WATO.

item:
 The description of the temperature sensor

discovery:
 One service is created for each sensor.
